# ShopFlow E-Commerce Platform

Modern full-stack e-commerce platform built with Next.js 14, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, and Stripe.

## Quick Links

- Live Demo: [Coming Soon]
- GitHub: https://github.com/filipmarinca/shopflow-ecommerce

## Key Features

### For Customers
- Browse products with search and filters
- Detailed product pages with images
- Shopping cart and checkout
- Stripe payment integration
- Order tracking
- User accounts
- Product reviews
- Wishlist

### For Admins
- Real-time dashboard with analytics
- Product management (CRUD)
- Order management
- Customer insights
- Inventory tracking
- Low stock alerts

## Built With

- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- PostgreSQL + Prisma
- NextAuth.js
- Stripe
- Vercel

